data.description: "BONUS ROOM" THIS CONDO HAS AN EXTRA ROOM WHICH COULD BE USED AS A STUDY, SECOND SITTING AREA OR EVEN A SECOND BEDROOM! Luxury high rise located in the heart of San Antonio, with easy access to the Tower of Americas, the Riverwalk and the Alamo. True Urban living Within walking distance from downtowns finest restaurants, shopping, family activities such as Hemisphere Park, and much more. Amazing amenities include a full-service, 24-hour concierge, a fitness center, conference room, business center, swimming pool, bbq grilling station,20th floor sky suite, & roof top deck. Beautiful oversized 1 bedroom/1.5 bathroom PLUS study at The Vidorra Condominium. This beautifully updated unit offers gorgeous hardwoods, granite countertops, glass tile backsplash in kitchen, stainless steel appliances, an abundance of storage, and more. Enjoy gorgeous tree-lined views with the City skyline in the background.
